my recipe
ingredients:
1 cup white sugar
1 cup lemon juice
1 cup water
2 to 3 cups cold water

step1:place the sugar and water in a pan and bring to a simmer.stir so that the sugar dissolves

step2:while the water is heating for the simple syrup,juice your lemons.

step3:pour juice and simple syrup sugar water into a serving pitcher.add 2 to 3 cups of cold water

step4:refrigerate 30 to 40 minutes
